fields.description: Hawaiian food is all about flavours that contrast and complement. Established back in 2019, Ohana Diner is a popular pioneer Hawaiian-style diner in Dhaka. Eventually, Ohana expanded its cuisine range, upholding the richness of seafood, meat and poultry with an aesthetic oceanic themed interior. Ohana strides and strives in creating signature dishes and unique recipes consistently to the satisfaction of its esteemed guests.
